{"id":257553,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-80余名上海民众再向市人大请愿要求诉权（/","date":"2012-10-16T18:15:56Z","modified":"2012-10-16T18:15:56Z","title":"维权网 | 80余名上海民众再向市人大请愿要求诉权（组图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>星期一下午，上海上访维权人士为了捍卫法律尊严、维护公民诉权，第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">72</span><span>次集体向上海市人大常务委员会请愿，这种公民行动已经坚持一年有余。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BKiHXk5mYPg/UH10344-5WI/AAAAAAAARSQ/izeYPF1L31o/s1600/72%E6%AC%A1%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E7%85%A71.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"185\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BKiHXk5mYPg/UH10344-5WI/AAAAAAAARSQ/izeYPF1L31o/s1600/72%E6%AC%A1%E9%9B%86%E4%BD%93%E7%85%A71.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-z__RJeTkBPA/UH109hxrTiI/AAAAAAAARSY/4V6W_MkadOg/s1600/72%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25BD%2593%25E7%2585%25A73.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"205\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-z__RJeTkBPA/UH109hxrTiI/AAAAAAAARSY/4V6W_MkadOg/s320/72%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25BD%2593%25E7%2585%25A73.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-yHtvEVCgALI/UH11CqzzwgI/AAAAAAAARSg/SrjRGlJXXiw/s1600/72%E6%AC%A1%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%AF%89%E6%9D%83%E7%99%BB%E8%AE%B0%E8%A1%A8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-yHtvEVCgALI/UH11CqzzwgI/AAAAAAAARSg/SrjRGlJXXiw/s320/72%E6%AC%A1%E7%BB%B4%E6%8A%A4%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E8%AF%89%E6%9D%83%E7%99%BB%E8%AE%B0%E8%A1%A8.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LebTkM2Ra4E/UH11LlX8BEI/AAAAAAAARSo/ZQrVjoSHZfM/s1600/%E7%AC%AC72%E6%AC%A1%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A1%B5.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-LebTkM2Ra4E/UH11LlX8BEI/AAAAAAAARSo/ZQrVjoSHZfM/s320/%E7%AC%AC72%E6%AC%A1%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E7%AC%AC1%E9%A1%B5.JPG\" width=\"222\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BhgWhCfOHBM/UH11VpE_nnI/AAAAAAAARSw/uQJmbjuYPZ4/s1600/%E7%AC%AC72%E6%AC%A1%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E7%AC%AC2%E9%A1%B5.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-BhgWhCfOHBM/UH11VpE_nnI/AAAAAAAARSw/uQJmbjuYPZ4/s320/%E7%AC%AC72%E6%AC%A1%E7%AD%BE%E5%90%8D%E5%8D%95%E7%AC%AC2%E9%A1%B5.JPG\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83</span><span>名上访维权人士为了维护上海</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1060</span><span>户家庭的切身利益，第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">72</span><span>次请求上海市人大常委会履行法定职责，追究三级法院剥夺公民诉权的违法行为。上海在征地、拆迁、拘留、劳教、医疗事故；劳动争议、司法不公等案件中，上海三级法院不作为，对当事人依法提起的诉讼既不立案、又不裁定。法院的法官不讲法，恶意剥夺公民应有的诉权，人大应该监督查处，人大应该追究渎职侵权的法官责任和法官的腐败行为，彻底清除上海市行政管辖区的一切行政不作为、乱作为的恶习，铲除一切腐败根源。上海上访维权人士已经第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">72</span><span>次集体请求上海市人大常委会保障公民应有的诉权。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当天有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83</span><span>名维权代表到场，推荐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>名代表是：刘淑珍、孙洪琴、孙建敏、乔纪花、周雪珍。得知是 费 老师在接待室接待，代表们把“我要立案”的希望寄托 于费 老师，充满信心地在信访大厅里排队等候。在等待中，没有等到叫号接待，却等来保安的驱赶。登记表和签名单也来不及提交，就被赶到门外，代表们在紧闭的大门外又一次希望变成失望。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>代表们和往日一样拍了集体照，以表示对维护公民诉权的决心和信心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与这次集体请愿行动的上海市民代表有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">83</span><span>人（登记表和签名单详见附图），希望引起人大领导高度重视。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>“我要立案——维护公民诉权”行动，请与下述市民代表联系：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13524687100</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>焦东海（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13801802454</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>鲁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">  </span><span>俊（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13651817422</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>赵迪迪（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13482668387</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>崔福芳（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13564097383</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>朱金娣（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13042111402</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>沈佩兰（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13764885120</span><span>）</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span>王扣玛（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13601929155</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>王蓉华（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13162424968</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>邱贵荣（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15001903401</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>刘洪贤（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13524850369</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>童国菁（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13917920278</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>郑培培（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">02153963826</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div><span>孙建敏（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13671947476</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>陈建芳（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15026516445</span><span>）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-831015718642910